{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "c3d4e5f6-a7b8-9012-cdef-123456789012",
    "name": "Chatbot UPRIT",
    "description": "Colección para testear el chatbot en producción: `https://chatbot.uprit.edu.pe`\n\n**Importar también:** `chatbot-uprit.postman_environment.json`\n\n**Antes de probar webhook POST:** configura `meta_webhook_verify_token` y `webhook_secret` en el environment (mismos valores que `.env` del servidor).\n\nEl script pre-request firma el body con HMAC-SHA256 (`x-hub-signature-256`) usando `webhook_secret`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "GET /health",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "",
              "pm.test('Body status ok', () => {",
              "    const json = pm.response.json();",
              "    pm.expect(json.status).to.eql('ok');",
              "    pm.expect(json.timestamp).to.be.a('string');",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "https://chatbot.uprit.edu.pe/health",
          "protocol": "https",
          "host": ["chatbot", "uprit", "edu", "pe"],
          "path": ["health"]
        },
        "description": "Health check de producción (`chatbot.uprit.edu.pe`)."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "GET /webhook — Meta verification",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "",
              "pm.test('Returns hub.challenge', () => {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.text()).to.eql(pm.environment.get('webhook_challenge'));",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "https://chatbot.uprit.edu.pe/webhook?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token={{meta_webhook_verify_token}}&hub.challenge={{webhook_challenge}}",
          "protocol": "https",
          "host": ["chatbot", "uprit", "edu", "pe"],
          "path": ["webhook"],
          "query": [
            { "key": "hub.mode", "value": "subscribe" },
            { "key": "hub.verify_token", "value": "{{meta_webhook_verify_token}}" },
            { "key": "hub.challenge", "value": "{{webhook_challenge}}" }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Handshake de Meta (mismo flujo que al conectar el webhook en Meta Developers).\n\nRequiere `meta_webhook_verify_token` = `META_WEBHOOK_VERIFY_TOKEN` del servidor."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "GET /webhook — Invalid token (403)",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 403', () => pm.response.to.have.status(403));"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [],
        "url": {
          "raw": "https://chatbot.uprit.edu.pe/webhook?hub.mode=subscribe&hub.verify_token=token_invalido&hub.challenge={{webhook_challenge}}",
          "protocol": "https",
          "host": ["chatbot", "uprit", "edu", "pe"],
          "path": ["webhook"],
          "query": [
            { "key": "hub.mode", "value": "subscribe" },
            { "key": "hub.verify_token", "value": "token_invalido" },
            { "key": "hub.challenge", "value": "{{webhook_challenge}}" }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Verifica que tokens incorrectos sean rechazados."
      },
      "response": []
    },
    {
      "name": "POST /webhook — Text message",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const secret = pm.environment.get('webhook_secret');",
              "",
              "if (!secret || secret.startsWith('TU_')) {",
              "    console.warn('Configura webhook_secret en el environment (WEBHOOK_SECRET del .env).');",
              "}",
              "",
              "const rawBody = pm.variables.replaceIn(pm.request.body.raw);",
              "const signature = CryptoJS.HmacSHA256(rawBody, secret).toString(CryptoJS.enc.Hex);",
              "",
              "pm.request.headers.upsert({",
              "    key: 'x-hub-signature-256',",
              "    value: 'sha256=' + signature",
              "});",
              "",
              "pm.request.body.update(rawBody);"
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test('Status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
              "",
              "pm.test('Responde rápido (Meta exige 200)', () => {",
              "    pm.expect(pm.response.responseTime).to.be.below(5000);",
              "});"
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"object\": \"whatsapp_business_account\",\n  \"entry\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"WHATSAPP_BUSINESS_ACCOUNT_ID\",\n      \"changes\": [\n        {\n          \"field\": \"messages\",\n          \"value\": {\n            \"messaging_product\": \"whatsapp\",\n            \"metadata\": {\n              \"display_phone_number\": \"15551234567\",\n              \"phone_number_id\": \"1234567890\"\n            },\n            \"contacts\": [\n              {\n                \"profile\": { \"name\": \"Postman Test\" },\n                \"wa_id\": \"{{test_wa_id}}\"\n              }\n            ],\n            \"messages\": [\n              {\n                \"from\": \"{{test_wa_id}}\",\n                \"id\": \"wamid.postman.test.001\",\n                \"timestamp\": \"1719900000\",\n                \"type\": \"text\",\n                \"text\": { \"body\": \"{{test_message}}\" }\n              }\n            ]\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "https://chatbot.uprit.edu.pe/webhook",
          "protocol": "https",
          "host": ["chatbot", "uprit", "edu", "pe"],
          "path": ["webhook"]
        },
        "description": "Simula un mensaje de texto entrante de WhatsApp en producción.\n\nEl pre-request script firma el body con `WEBHOOK_SECRET`.\n\n**Nota:** dispara el flujo real (IA + respuesta WhatsApp)."
      },
      "response": []
    },
